802
01:47:49,240 --> 01:47:55,800
[SPEAKER_01] The boiler house was located in the courtyard of one of the tenement houses on Balassi-Bálint Street, that is, on the street leading towards Jászai-Mariáter.

803
01:47:55,900 --> 01:48:01,660
[SPEAKER_01] and essentially, a tunnel from the boiler house brought the heat to the parliament building.

804
01:48:01,720 --> 01:48:08,080
[SPEAKER_01] There was a need for this because during the planning, they told Steinlein that building such a neo-Gothic structure

