816
01:49:13,400 --> 01:49:16,560
[SPEAKER_01] The metro itself, by the way, is a nuclear-proof bomb shelter, and to this day it is, in fact, a civil defense facility,

817
01:49:16,600 --> 01:49:21,840
[SPEAKER_01] and the metro has, or had, the property that it was, so to speak, rerouted here to Kossuth Square afterwards,

818
01:49:21,840 --> 01:49:31,600
