820
01:49:36,240 --> 01:49:49,020
[SPEAKER_01] hanem az évszázadok óta meglévő közlekedési vonalat követve, hogy az Erzsébet híd alatt átmenve, ugye Krisztinavároson keresztül érte volna el a Várhegy mögött az Észak-Budai részt,

821
01:49:49,040 --> 01:49:50,900
[SPEAKER_01] but because the parliament building is located here,

822
01:49:50,900 --> 01:49:56,760
[SPEAKER_01] the plans were modified accordingly, and the metro was redirected in this direction, back when it was still on the drawing board.

823
01:49:56,980 --> 01:50:04,260
[SPEAKER_01] Indeed, shelters were built in connection with the metro, which were told to the workers that they were building the metro,

824
01:50:04,280 --> 01:50:15,280
[SPEAKER_01] but in reality, a separate nuclear-proof shelter was built, but this is located under, or connected to, the party headquarters on Akadémia Street, and not the parliament.

825
01:50:15,380 --> 01:50:19,220
[SPEAKER_01] And, of course, the parliament does not have such a connection,

826
01:50:19,220 --> 01:50:28,960
