01:50:47,880 --> 01:50:50,500
[SPEAKER_01] but these were not nuclear-proof shelters.

831
01:50:50,580 --> 01:51:02,720
[SPEAKER_01] I don't know about a connection to the metro, but there is a connection that was built recently, the building above the metro, which was renovated quite significantly recently,

832
01:51:02,720 --> 01:51:17,840
[SPEAKER_01] so it was demolished, and a new building was constructed over the metro exit, and this building, the Szabadgyörgy office building, has an underground tunnel, which connects it, and this is not a secret, it is publicly known, connecting it to the parliament building.

833
01:51:17,880 --> 01:51:30,060
[SPEAKER_01] The practical reason for this, of course, is that the staff of the parliamentary office work in that building, and I understand that the Tisza faction is also going to move in there,

834
01:51:30,100 --> 01:51:43,720
[SPEAKER_01] and the practical reason is simply that when someone enters the secure zone, they can pass through to the building without having to exit and re-enter.

835
01:51:43,840 --> 01:51:47,740
