836
01:51:47,880 --> 01:51:56,820
[SPEAKER_01] With other parts, and I should also add that outside the building, the visitor center and the underground garage of the parliament are located on the building's night side.

837
01:51:56,900 --> 01:52:08,700
[SPEAKER_01] Naturally, these are connected to the building, and there are three points where you can pass through. Tourists have one or two passageways, and the parliamentary staff have another.

838
01:52:09,140 --> 01:52:14,800
[SPEAKER_11] I really feel a bit like it's good that we came here today, beyond the amazing things happening in the parliament building,

839
01:52:14,800 --> 01:52:23,480
