842
01:52:44,780 --> 01:52:53,640
[SPEAKER_11] how this works, how they came up with this idea, how practical it was, and, by the way, how well the cooling actually works inside, since there are no air conditioners on the walls, as we can see.

843
01:52:53,760 --> 01:53:00,660
[SPEAKER_01] We now find ourselves in a delicate situation where an art historian has to speak interestingly about building engineering issues, but I'll try.

