1273
02:40:09,770 --> 02:40:16,330
[SPEAKER_13] The relevant proposal can be accessed on the IT network under number S-12.

1274
02:40:17,370 --> 02:40:22,250
[SPEAKER_13] Honored National Assembly, according to the fourth paragraph of Article 16 of the Fundamental Law,

1275
02:40:22,250 --> 02:40:28,850
[SPEAKER_13] the election of the Prime Minister requires the votes of more than half of the members of the National Assembly.

1276
02:40:29,730 --> 02:40:32,590
[SPEAKER_13] The Prime Minister assumes office upon election.

1277
02:40:32,770 --> 02:40:35,290
[SPEAKER_13] I call upon the Honored National Assembly.

1278
02:40:36,050 --> 02:40:40,990
[SPEAKER_13] Shall Hungarian Péter be elected as Prime Minister of Hungary?

1279
02:40:41,770 --> 02:40:43,310
[SPEAKER_13] I ask you to vote now!

1280
02:40:54,710 --> 02:40:56,950
[SPEAKER_13] I shall announce the decision.

1281
02:40:57,130 --> 02:41:05,070
[SPEAKER_13] The National Assembly voted 140 in favor, 54 against, and 1 abstention.

1282
02:41:06,050 --> 02:41:11,170
[SPEAKER_13] Hungarian Péter was elected Prime Minister of Hungary.

1283
02:41:13,670 --> 02:41:15,150
[UNKNOWN] Thank you very much.

1284
