[SPEAKER_13] Honorable National Assembly! The solemn oath-taking is now to follow.

1285
02:42:02,910 --> 02:42:09,350
[SPEAKER_13] I ask you to stand up as we pay respects before the national flag and the historical flags are brought in.

1286
