1506
03:10:11,550 --> 03:10:16,510
[SPEAKER_16] One of the most important institutions of the 2026 system change will be.

1507
03:10:16,590 --> 03:10:33,390
[SPEAKER_16] Its task will be to uncover the abuses of public property in the past twenty years, to investigate corrupt and asset-stripping schemes,

1508
03:10:33,390 --> 03:10:46,290
[SPEAKER_16] to support criminal proceedings and to act with every legal means to recover public assets obtained unlawfully.

1509
03:10:46,510 --> 03:11:01,410
[SPEAKER_16] The office will not be a political tool subordinated to the government. It will operate as an autonomous, independent state body, which will only be accountable to the National Assembly.

1510
03:11:01,410 --> 03:11:16,950
[SPEAKER_16] Its independence, professionalism, and transparency are important because only when the institution itself is based on the rule of law can the pursuit of truth be credible.

1511
03:11:17,330 --> 03:11:28,890
[UNKNOWN] The office will uncover the state procurement system, concession agreements, public assets outsourced to foundations,

1512
03:11:28,890 --> 03:11:51,530
[SPEAKER_16] the overpricing of state investments, abuses of EU funds, financial schemes linked to the Hungarian National Bank, the financial flows of the TAO system, private equity funds, offshore-based schemes,

1513
03:11:51,730 --> 03:11:57,970
[SPEAKER_16] as well as any transactions where the violation of public property is suspected.

1514
03:11:58,890 --> 03:12:10,550
[SPEAKER_16] Suspected abuse of office, mismanagement, money laundering, budget fraud, or asset stripping.

1515
03:12:24,390 --> 03:12:28,450
[SPEAKER_16] Where criminal liability arises, it will be the office.

1516
03:12:28,890 --> 03:12:35,810
[SPEAKER_16] It will prepare and support the work of investigative and judicial bodies.

1517
03:12:36,110 --> 03:12:49,130
[SPEAKER_16] Where it is possible to recover assets through civil law, it will initiate claims for compensation, restitution of unjust enrichment, recovery of unjustified benefits, and asset freezes.

1518
03:12:49,570 --> 03:12:57,150
[SPEAKER_16] Where assets have been taken abroad, it will seek international legal assistance and cooperation.

1519
03:12:58,890 --> 03:13:07,890
[SPEAKER_16] Where foreign entities, concessions, or foundation-based schemes violate the public interest, it will challenge them legally.

1520
03:13:08,170 --> 03:13:27,150
[SPEAKER_16] I would like to state clearly: anyone who believes that political connections, party loyalty, personal loyalty, or old power protection can provide immunity from law violations,

1521
03:13:27,270 --> 03:13:28,270
[SPEAKER_16] abuses will be addressed.

1522
03:13:28,890 --> 03:13:34,330
[SPEAKER_16] Anyone who believes they can escape the consequences of actions against public property is gravely mistaken.

1523
03:13:34,910 --> 03:13:39,690
[SPEAKER_16] Hungary will no longer be a country without consequences.

1524
03:14:01,710 --> 03:14:07,050
[SPEAKER_16] What belongs to the nation must serve the nation.

1525
03:14:07,370 --> 03:14:13,190
[UNKNOWN] What was illegally taken away will be lawfully recovered.

1526
03:14:13,350 --> 03:14:17,150
[SPEAKER_16] What was concealed will be brought to light.

1527
03:14:17,310 --> 03:14:22,850
[SPEAKER_16] What was committed will be investigated and exposed.

1528
03:14:23,650 --> 03:14:27,990
[SPEAKER_16] Those responsible will be held accountable for their actions.

1529
