[SPEAKER_16] [SPEAKER_16] it did not succeed.

1554
03:16:54,650 --> 03:16:56,230
[SPEAKER_16] [SPEAKER_16] It did not happen.

1555
03:16:56,950 --> 03:17:08,490
[SPEAKER_16] [SPEAKER_16] It did not succeed, for example, when Viktor Orbán, the defeated prime minister, referred to half the country as a pest to be exterminated.

1556
03:17:09,470 --> 03:17:22,550
[SPEAKER_16] [SPEAKER_16] Mr. President, it did not succeed when Viktor Orbán or even the president of the Curia threatened judges or artists, persecuted them,

1557
03:17:22,550 --> 03:17:33,730
[SPEAKER_16] [SPEAKER_16] and it did not succeed either, Mr. President, when one should have stood up for the underage children ruined in the child protection system.

1558
03:17:33,810 --> 03:17:45,890
[SPEAKER_16] [SPEAKER_16] And it did not succeed either when the now defeated government sent secret services against the largest opposition party.

